By Krystyna Neumao
A combination of refined, cool matters and militanoy, of leading participation within the us. governmental
system and protest tactics outside it
make Julian Bond a unique leader in
American peace and civil rights
strengths.
A few years back the hardcore Mr.
Bond became one of the few degrees
